{"tid":2126494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有肺炎唔代表唔駛做任務！過嚟睇下今日有咩行動啦！","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T01:17:58.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"266c69c3752ceec08e0a2dade088c7dd35c1c668","tid":2126494,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"首先麻煩咁多位sub咗文宣channel先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個channel好耐歷史但只有八萬幾sub<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HK_Schedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_Schedule&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=a0ed5f29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_Schedule</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">是日活動一：寄信俾手足</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋宣傳下我地嘅政府有幾咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQpgpqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQpgpqT.jpg&h=58c3bb54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUMB8Sz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUMB8Sz.jpg&h=28a158a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzotfxz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqzotfxz.jpg&h=1c5ab6e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#27Jul 今日7月27日 (一)  日程<br />\n武漢肺炎確診數目仍然過百確診 , 種種跡象顯示是政府的&quot;天才&quot;防疫政策導致爆發😡 , 另外請大家亦要多關注還押/入獄手足 , 因為現時因疫情關係探訪次數大減 , 令到他們心情情緒也變得比較低落😢希望大家都參與「和你做筆友」活動 , 默默鼓勵他們🙏<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n🏛是日暫沒有日程 , 請大家密切留意日程有否突發活動 , 另外每日亦有被捕手足上庭 , 有時間可以幫忙送車及聲援👉被捕人士關注組👈<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">是日活動二：全民聯署夾爆政府</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnArMFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnArMFM.jpg&h=2e34d490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【全民聯署夾爆政府】<br />\n聯署網址：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/FTToozPmEbFnDD316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FFTToozPmEbFnDD316&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9ef83f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/FTToozPmEbFnDD316</a><br />\n<br />\n現時聯署已有7000多人，香港人要繼續努力！<br />\n再重提我哋嘅訴求：<br />\n1. 反對醫管局大會無視前線員工壓力而作出凍薪決定。<br />\n2. 反對中國抗疫團隊來港執業，以保障香港醫療專業水平。<br />\n3. 於疫症爆發期間，每位前線員工皆面對沉重的工作壓力。醫管局應一視同仁，向每位於臨床病區員工包括於化驗室員工發放緊急級別津貼。<br />\n4. 醫管局必須確保於高風險區工作的員工有供自我隔離的住宿，避免同事受酒店無禮對待的不愉快事件再度發生。<br />\n<br />\n**你的聯署資料只會用作數據分析並完全保密。<br />\n**每人只可簽署一次，因此需要登入google。<br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\nTelegram Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/ha_employalliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fha_employalliance&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=f906048b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ha_employalliance</a><br />\n👇🏻加入會員專屬telegram群組👇🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/y7ai3AWXNcvAzuYJ7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fy7ai3AWXNcvAzuYJ7&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=894d825a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/y7ai3AWXNcvAzuYJ7</a><br />\n📌罷工秋後算帳及工作環境問題，請電郵本會：<br />\ninfo@haea.org.hk"},{"pid":"8418c1b2e13145ee8d2ed783b24d43d8e9b92463","tid":2126494,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"765aedd63507fef9725e3e50eee33b9e5c09a5c5","tid":2126494,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}